p%3EIt%20was%20a%20shocker%20to%20learn%20that%20because%20we%20live%20how%20we%20live%2C%20they%20live%20differently%2C%20like%20they%20are%20in%20their%20own%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20interesting%20to%20go%20there%20and%20hear%20about%20my%20country%20from%20their%20perspective%20because%20our%20ways%20of%20life%20were%20so%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20North%20Korean%20kids%20didn't%20have%20phones%2C%20and%20even%20we%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20use%20phones%20in%20the%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20internet%20network%2C%20but%20they%20had%20service%2C%20so%20we%20could%20call%20through%20landlines.%20It%20was%20like%20taking%20a%20network%20break.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bb43657-249b-437c-8e4e-672ea62b940e%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20at%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20came%20out%20of%20the%20camp%20for%20visits%20in%20Pyongyang%2C%20North%20Korean%20civilians%20came%20and%20talked%20to%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20reminded%20me%20of%20home.%20If%20you%20come%20to%20Tanzania%2C%20people%20are%20going%20to%20come%20and%20talk%20to%20you.%20They're%20going%20to%20want%20to%20get%20to%20know%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20camp%2C%20all%20the%20nationalities%20were%20kept%20apart%2C%20and%20we%20only%20mixed%20during%20activities%20that%20were%20arranged%20for%20all%20of%20us%2C%20like%20performances%20and%20competitions%20in%20cooking%2C%20swimming%2C%20marathons%2C%20and%20more.%20We%20also%20met%20during%20leisure%20activities%20such%20as%20swimming%20and%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20competed%20in%20the%20cooking%20competition%20and%20won.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221170%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Regina%20Beraldo%20Kihwele%20and%20her%20friends%20won%20the%20cooking%20competition%20at%20North%20Korea's%20Songdowon%20International%20Children's%20Camp%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202016.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a0c25f2d66759f66fda076%3F