%20how%20to%20make%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-going-after-amazon-with-ecommerce-strategy-from-target-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelivery%20to%20customers%20work.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Domino's%2C%20the%20pizza%20chain%20known%20for%20delivery%2C%20is%20having%20success%20drawing%20customers%20to%20its%20restaurants%20to%20pick%20up%20their%20own%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20carryout%20business%20is%20on%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Russell%20Weiner%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20we%20didn't%20even%20contemplate%20years%20ago.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20business%20was%20a%20bright%20spot%20for%20Domino's%20during%20its%20second%20quarter.%20The%20company's%20carryout%20comparable%20sales%20grew%207.9%25%2C%20while%20delivery%20comparable%20sales%20rose%202.7%25%20during%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20who%20order%20for%20delivery%20and%20those%20who%20stop%20by%20a%20restaurant%20to%20carry%20their%20orders%20out%20are%20mostly%20two%20separate%20groups%20with%20different%20priorities%2C%20Weiner%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelivery%20is%20about%20convenience%2C%20and%20customers%20who%20order%20their%20food%20for%20delivery%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20the%20extra%20fees%20and%20tip%20their%20driver%2C%20he%20said.%20Besides%20operating%20its%20own%20delivery%20service%2C%20Domino's%20also%20offers%20delivery%20through%20Uber.%20The%20third-party%20service%20accounts%20for%20roughly%203%25%20of%20Domino's%20sales%2C%20Weiner%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20see%20only%20about%2015%25%20overlap%20between%20our%20carryout%20and%20delivery%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20other%2C%20more%20budget-conscious%20consumers%20realize%20that%20they%20can%20get%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%20another%20pizza%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20money%20they%20spend%20on%20delivery%20fees%20and%20tips%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20delivery%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bexpensive%20convenience%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20US%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDelivery%20services%20gained%20popularity%20during%20the%20pandemic%20as%20consumers%20stayed%20at%20home%20and%20had%20everything%20from%20a%20restaurant%20meal%20to%20electronics%20delivered%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20DoorDash%2C%20Instacart%2C%20Uber%20Eats%2C%20Walmart%20Spark%2C%20and%20other%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20society%20reopened%20and%20prices%20soared%20for%20many%20consumer%20goods%2C%20especially%20food%2C%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freturn-to-work-mandates-could-mean-more-trouble-for-instacart-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecustomers%20cut%20back%20on%20their%20delivery%20habits.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Some%20also%20realized%20that%20they%20were%20paying%20a%20big%20premium%20to%20have%20stuff%20brought%20to%20their%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstacart-shoppers-forbidden-from-giving-customers-paper-receipts-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOne%20Instacart%20customer%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20TikTok%20after%20realizing%20that%20she%20had%20paid%20close%20to%20%24100%20in%20markups%20on%20her%20groceries%20%E2%80%94%20excluding%20delivery%20fees%20and%20a%20tip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20people%20are%20also%20opting%20to%20drive%20to%20their%20local%20Domino's%20and%20pick%20up%20orders%20themselves%20for%20another%20reason%3A%20Control.%20Many%20carryout%20customers%20prefer%20the%20option%20over%20delivery%20because%20they're%20worried%20about%20what%20they'll%20have%20to%20do%20if%20something%20is%20wrong%20with%20their%20delivery%20order%20or%20whether%20it%20will%20show%20up%20in%20time%20for%20a%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20person's%20like%2C%20'I%20don't%20care%20if%20it's%20out%20of%20my%20way%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20pick%20it%20up%20because%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20right%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20completely%20different%20customer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDomino's%20has%20also%20attracted%20many%20new%20carryout%20customers%20by%20opening%20more%20restaurants%20and%20cutting%20the%20distance%20that%20customers%20have%20to%20drive%2C%20thus%20making%20picking%20up%20an%20order%20less%20of%20a%20hassle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20want%20to%20drive%20past%20three%20or%20four%20pizza%20places%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Domino's%20customers.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20the%20first%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20work%20in%20the%20restaurant%20industry%20and%20have%20a%20story%20idea%20to%20share%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20this%20reporter%20at%20abitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdominos-customers-increasingly-picking-up-pizzas-amid-high-delivery-costs-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722073622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a284992d66759f66fe58df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdominos-customers-increasingly-picking-up-pizzas-amid-high-delivery-costs-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Domino's%20CEO%20said%20that%20its%20carryout%20business%20is%20booming%20--%20and%20its%20shows%20why%20many%20consumers%20aren't%20interested%20in%20having%20pizza%20delivered.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdominos-customers-increasingly-picking-up-pizzas-amid-high-delivery-costs-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20Laos%20unveil%20world's%20first%20stamp%20featuring%20Ram%20Lalla%20of%20Ayodhya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A17220734480