-with-regulations-for-short-term-rentals-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elicensing%20requirements%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0for%20short-term%20rentals%20that%20restrict%20the%20number%20in%20any%20given%20area%20and%20impose%20tax%20collections.%20But%20not%20everyone%20plays%20by%20those%20rules%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20listing%20agents%20on%20behalf%20of%20sellers%20promote%20this%20revenue%20stream%20on%20houses%20that%20don't%20have%20the%20required%20license%20%E2%80%94%20and%20aren't%20even%20eligible%20for%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20and%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.courier-journal.com%2Fstory%2Flife%2Fhome-garden%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2Fairbnb-superhost-louisville-dana-mcmahan-expert%2F427790002%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20the%20legal%20%3C%2Fa%3Epermits%20and%20licenses%20for%20my%20home%2C%20I%20think%20this%20practice%20is%20pretty%20unsavory%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20from%20a%20profession%20that's%20supposed%20to%20have%20strict%20ethical%20guidelines.%20Even%20when%20the%20listing%20truly%20does%20have%20legal%20income%20potential%2C%20it's%20not%20a%20magic%20bullet%20or%20a%20fast%20path%20to%20riches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22little%20carriage%20house%20on%20the%20alley%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d7f9c792e22af078b4837f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELittle%20Carriage%20House%20on%20the%20Alley.%3Cp%3EPhoto%20by%20Diane%20Deaton%20Street%20for%20Airbnb%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20rentals%20can%20be%20considered%20passive%20by%20IRS%20definitions%2C%20but%20here's%20the%20truth%20from%20someone%20who's%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20more%20than%2015%20years%3A%20rentals%20are%20endless%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20the%20cleaning%2C%20or%20calendar%20management%2C%20or%20the%20trying%20to%20delight%20guests%20or%2