at%20different%20times%20of%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20that%20America's%207-Elevens%20were%20at%20one%20point%20only%20receiving%20two%20deliveries%20per%20week%2C%20with%20many%20items%20being%20ordered%20that%20consumers%20had%20little%20to%20no%20interest%20in.%20That%20was%20clearly%20a%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican%20consumers%20can%20expect%20to%20see%20products%20on%20shelves%20at%20their%20local%207-Elevens%20that%20they%20might%20previously%20have%20had%20to%20venture%20all%20the%20way%20to%20Japan%20to%20buy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20fresher%20variety%20of%20options%20that%20meet%20the%20tastes%20of%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%207-Eleven%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20was%20working%20with%20its%20partners%20in%20Japan%20to%20%26quot%3Bintroduce%20new%20items%20like%20chicken%20teriyaki%20rice%20balls%2C%20miso%20ramen%2C%20and%20sweet%20chili%20crisp%20wings%20to%20US%20customers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20constantly%20evolving%20the%20fresh%20food%20assortment%20in%20our%20stores%2C%20tailoring%20the%20offerings%20at%20each%20location%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20and%20preferences%20of%20local%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20user%20%40greenonionbun%2C%20based%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC90uXtYy38p%2F%3Figsh%3DMTYxaDk3bXlpYjlzOQ%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eposted%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20a%20trip%20she%20said%20she'd%20taken%20to%20a%20local%207-Eleven%20after%20hearing%20that%20the%20convenience%20store%20chain%20was%20going%20to%20start%20stocking%20Japanese%20snacks%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20egg%20sandwiches%20seemed%20more%20Japanese-style%20as%20they%20were%20made%20with%20fluffy%20milk%20bread%2C%20for%20example%2C%20but%20there%20were%20subtle%20differences%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGood%20news%