y%2C%20described%20it%20as%20police%20brutality%20against%20people%20from%20BAME%20(British%20Asian%20and%20minority%20ethnic)%20backgrounds.%20A%20few%20people%20took%20to%20streets%20to%20protest%20the%20police%20action%20as%20the%20incident%20reminded%20them%20of%20the%20George%20Floyd%20assault%20in%202020%2C%20which%20spurred%20the%20Black%20Lives%20Matter%20movement%20across%20the%20West.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERacism%2C%20discrimination%2C%20and%20misogyny%20within%20Britain's%20police%20forces%20are%20pervasive.%20Last%20year%2C%20after%20a%20year-long%20official%20review%20of%20London's%20Met%20Police%2C%20reviewer%20Baroness%20Casey%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20force%20suffers%20from%20institutional%20racism%2C%20misogyny%2C%20and%20homophobia%26quot%3B%2C%20further%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20time%20for%20the%20force%20not%20to%20be%20in%20denial%20about%20these%20deep-rooted%20issues''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Many%20Types%20Of%20Racism%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERacism%20is%20not%20a%20feature%20limited%20to%20the%20police%20forces%20alone%20in%20the%20UK.%20Several%20recent%20official%20reports%20have%20highlighted%20racism%20in%20some%20premier%20British%20institutions%2C%20including%20the%20BBC%2C%20the%20armed%20forces%2C%20and%20various%20government%20offices.%20All%20of%20these%20are%20controlled%20primarily%20by%20White%20males.%20For%20non-Whites%2C%20reaching%20top%20positions%20in%20these%20institutions%20is%20next%20to%20impossible%2C%20and%20if%20at%20all%20that%20happens%2C%20it's%20mostly%20just%20tokenism.%20Greg%20Dyke%2C%20former%20director-general%20of%20the%20BBC%2C%20famously%20said%20in%202001%20that%20the%20media%20house%20was%20%26quot%3Bhideously%20White%26quot%3B%2C%20highlighting%20the%20lack%20of%20diversity%20within%20its%20workforce%20at%20the%20time.%20His%20comment%20sparked%20a%20broader%20conversation%20about%20the%20representation%20of%20ethnic%20minorities%20in%20British%20media%20and%20other%20institutions.%20True%2C%20some%20improvements%20have%20been%20made%20since%20then%2C%20but%20not%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fracism-reducing-my-desire-to-play-football-brazils-vinicius-junior-5311569%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0Racism%20Reducing%20My%20Desire%20To%20Play%20Football%3A%20Brazil's%20Vinicius%20Junior%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20overt%20racism%20too%2C%20which%20comes%20alive%20during%20the%2010%20months%20of%20the%20football%20season%20(August-May)%20across%20Europe.%20I%20am%20a%20football%20fanatic%20and%20an%20avid%20follower%20of%20European%20club%20football%3B%20not%20only%20have%20I%20witnessed%20racism%20first-hand%20in%20and%20outside%20stadiums%2C%20but%20I%20have%20also%20been%20at%20the%20receiving%20end%20of%20it.%20After%20being%20called%20a%20%26quot%3BPaki%26quot%3B%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bchutney%26quot%3B%20on%20occasion%2C%20%C2%A0I%20now%20prefer%20to%20watch%20matches%20on%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20there%20is%20little%20guarantee%20you%20will%20be%20spared%20because%20you%20are%20watching%20the%20match%20in%20the%20company%20of%20your%20White%20mates.%20But%20even%20as%20I%20say%20so%2C%20I've%20managed%20to%20escape%20the%20worst%20of%20racism.%20Think%20of%20those%20Black%20players%20who%20suffer%20humiliation%20and%20inhuman%20treatment%20from%20fans%20of%20rival%20teams%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20Some%20call%20them%20%26quot%3Bmonkeys%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20throw%20bananas%20at%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EColonialism%2C%20Slavery%20and%20Subjugation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhite%2C%20western%20racism%20has%20persisted%20for%20decades%2C%20even%20centuries.%20The%20Western%20hemisphere%20calls%20itself%20'civilised'%2C%20a%20notion%20perpetuated%20by%20media%2C%20writers%2C%20academics%20and%20leaders%2C%20who%20position%20themselves%20as%20champions%20of%20bringing%20'civilisation'%20to%20third-world%20countries.%20One%20form%20of%20that%20'civilising'%20role%20was%20donned%20by%20religious%20missionaries%20long%20ago%2C%20who%20believed%20the%20people%20outside%20of%20Christendom%20needed%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bled%20to%20the%20right%20path%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorical%20figures%20like%20Rudyard%20Kipling%20and%20Winston%20Churchill%20have%20espoused%20these%20ideas.%20The%20former's%20The%20White%20Man's%20Burden%20promoted%20this%20self-espoused%20'colonial%20duty'%20to%20civilise%20colonised%20societies.%20Churchill%20once%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20admit%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20a%20great%20wrong%20has%20been%20done%20to%20the%20Red%20Indians%20of%20America%2C%20or%20the%20black%20people%20of%20Australia...%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20stronger%20race%2C%20a%20higher%20grade%20race...%20has%20come%20in%20and%20taken%20their%20place.%26quot%3B%20Churchill%2C%20who%20is%20seen%20in%20India%20as%20racist%20and%20imperialist%2C%20is%20Britain's%20-%20more%20specifically%20England's%20national%20hero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwith-kamala-harris-democrats-would-bet-against-us-history-of-sexism-racism-6157603%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0With%20Kamala%20Harris%2C%20Democrats%20Would%20Bet%20Against%20US%20History%20Of%20Sexism%2C%20Racism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20Viktor%20Orban%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Hungary%2C%20said%20in%202019%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20the%20guardians%20of%20a%20civilisation%20that%20has%20been%20developed%20over%20millennia...%20We%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20have%20built%20the%20modern%20world%2C%20who%20have%20built%20the%20West%2C%20who%20have%20built%20the%20European%20Union.%20We%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20have%20written%20the%20rulebook%20of%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20The%20statement%20does%20not%20only%20reflect%20Hungarian%20Prime%20Minister's%20arrogance%20but%20also%20exposes%20him%20as%20an%20ignorant%20fool.%20Sadly%2C%20this%20arrogance%20is%20endemic%20in%20the%20West.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWestern%20Hypocrisy%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20same%20context%2C%20the%20speech%20made%20by%20US%20President%20George%20W.%20Bush%20in%20November%202003%20during%20his%20official%20visit%20to%20London%20was%20interesting.%20%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20and%20Great%20Britain%20share%20a%20mission%3A%20to%20bring%20the%20values%20of%20freedom%20and%20democracy%20to%20the%20world...%20We%20will%20not%20be%20deterred.%20We%20will%20not%20be%20defeated.%20We%20will%20bring%20freedom%20and%20civilisation%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBush's%20comments%20came%20several%20months%20after%20the%20invasion%20of%20Iraq%20in%20March%202003.%20The%20two%20%26quot%3Bcivilised%26quot%3B%20nations%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%2C%20had%20invaded%20a%20faraway%20country%20to%20civilise%20its%20people%20by%20implanting%20democracy%20there%20and%20imparting%20Western%20values.%20However%2C%20getting%20rid%20of%20weapons%20of%20mass%20destruction%20was%20the%20rationale%20presented%20to%20the%20world.%20The%20entire%20Western%20media%20jumped%20on%20to%20the%20'civilising'%20narrative%2C%20completely%20disregarding%20their%20duty%20to%20question%20the%20real%20reason%20behind%20the%20invasion.%20Ultimately%2C%20no%20weapons%20of%20mass%20destruction%20were%20found.%20It%20was%20all%20a%20pack%20of%20lies%2C%20spread%20by%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20civilised%20country%20in%20the%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'The%20Greatest%2C%20The%20Most%20Powerful'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20can%20forget%20the%20gaffe%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20-%20the%20commander%20in%20chief%20of%20the%20world's%20deadliest%20military%20force%20and%20the%20President%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20country%20-%20when%20he%20mistakenly