gster%20networks%2C%20radical%20groups%2C%20and%20terrorist%20organisations%20to%20execute%20a%20devastating%20attack%20during%20the%20pilgrimage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20there%20are%20alarming%20reports%20that%20ISI%20is%20using%20Babbar%20Khalsa%20International%20to%20target%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20Hindu%20figures%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20intelligence%20alert%20also%20noted%20the%20presence%20of%20suspected%20terrorists%20armed%20with%20advanced%20weaponry%20in%20a%20village%20near%20Pathankot%20in%20June.%20This%20intelligence%20led%20to%20an%20immediate%20search%20operation%20in%20Pathankot%20following%20the%20sighting%20of%20seven%20suspicious%20individuals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20disturbing%20development%2C%20a%20Hindu%20preacher%20in%20Punjab%20recently%20received%20a%20threat%20letter%20from%20a%20group%20claiming%20allegiance%20to%20Khalistan.%20The%20Punjab%20Police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20and%20initiated%20a%20search%20for%20the%20perpetrators%20behind%20this%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%204%20lakh%20devotees%20have%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Amarnath%20Yatra%20over%20the%20last%2028%20days.%20The%20cave%20shrine%20houses%20an%20ice%20stalagmite%20that%20wanes%20and%20waxes%20with%20the%20phases%20of%20the%20moon.%20Devotees%20believe%20that%20this%20structure%20symbolises%20the%20mythical%20powers%20of%20Lord%20Shiva.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cave%20is%20situated%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%203%2C888%20metres%20above%20the%20sea%20level%20in%20Kashmir.%20Devotees%20approach%20the%20cave%20shrine%20either%20from%20the%20traditional%20south%20Kashmir%20(Pahalgam)%20route%20or%20the%20north%20Kashmir%20(Baltal)%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pahalgam-cave%20shrine%20axis%20is%2048%20km%20long%20and%20it%20takes%20Yatris%20four%20to%20five%20days%20to%20reach%20the%20shrine.%20The%20Baltal-cave%20shrine%20axis%20is%2014%20km%20long%20and%20it%20takes%20one%20day%20for%