ald%20Trump%20falsely%20accused%20election%20rival%20Kamala%20Harris%20of%20being%20an%20anti-Semite%20who%20plans%20to%20allow%20the%20murder%20of%20newborn%20babies%2C%20in%20a%20speech%20meant%20to%20rally%20religious%20supporters%20Friday%20that%20quickly%20went%20off%20the%20rails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president%2C%20who%20is%20married%20to%20a%20Jewish%20man%2C%20has%20gained%20ground%20on%20Trump%20in%20polling%20since%20she%20replaced%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Democratic%20ticket%20just%20days%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Republican%20president%20Trump%20dedicated%20much%20of%20his%20address%20at%20a%20religious%20convention%20in%20southern%20Florida%20to%20assailing%20Harris's%20record%20as%20a%20senator%20and%20as%20Biden's%20number%20two%2C%20but%20many%20of%20his%20attacks%20were%20smears%20untethered%20to%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%2059-year-old%20Harris%20had%20skipped%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyau's%20speech%20to%20the%20US%20Congress%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20instead%20honour%20a%20prior%20commitment%2C%20Trump%20accused%20her%2C%20baselessly%2C%20of%20anti-Semitism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20doesn't%20like%20Jewish%20people.%20She%20doesn't%20like%20Israel.%20That's%20the%20way%20it%20is%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20way%20it's%20always%20going%20to%20be.%20She's%20not%20going%20to%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remark%20--%20coupled%20with%20his%20claim%20that%20Harris%20%26quot%3Bis%20totally%20against%20the%20Jewish%20people%26quot%3B%20in%20North%20Carolina%20on%20Wednesday%20--%20marked%20an%20escalation%20in%20Trump's%20incendiary%20rhetoric%2C%20days%20after%20his%20campaign%20said%20an%20attempt%20on%20his%20life%20had%20given%20him%20a%20focus%20on%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hour-long%20Friday%20speech%2C%20hosted%20by%20hard-right%20Turning%20Point%20Action%2C%20raised%20legitimate%20questions%20over%20Harris's%20previous%20statements%20on%20policing%2C%20immigration%20and%20the%20environment%20that%20placed%20her%20to%20the%20left%20of%20current%20Biden%20administration%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20marked%20by%20hyperbole%20and%20falsehood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Execute%20the%20baby'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20--%20a%20convicted%20felon%20who%20is%20fighting%20multiple%20further%20indictments%20--%20suggested%20baselessly%20that%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20FBI%20were%20%26quot%3Brounding%20up%26quot%3B%20Christians%20and%20anti-abortion%20activists%20and%20throwing%20them%20in%20jail%20for%20their%20%26quot%3Breligious%20beliefs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20called%20Biden's%20decision%20to%20exit%20the%20election%20campaign%20a%20%26quot%3Bcoup%26quot%3B%20by%20Democrats%20and%20said%20America%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Blaughing%20stock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20saved%20his%20darkest%20vitriol%20for%20Harris%2C%20calling%20her%20a%20%26quot%3Bbum%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20failed%20vice%20president%20who%20had%20rejected%20federal%20judges%20for%20being%20Catholic%20and%20would%20appoint%20%26quot%3Bhardcore%20Marxists%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20accused%20her%20falsely%20of%20wanting%20to%20force%20doctors%20to%20give%20chemical%20castration%20drugs%20to%20children%20and%20suggested%20she%20might%20cheat%20to%20win%20in%20November.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20Kamala%20Harris%20has%20her%20way%2C%20they%20will%20have%20a%20federal%20law%20for%20abortion%2C%20to%20rip%20the%20baby%20out%20of%20the%20womb%20in%20the%20eighth%2C%20ninth%20month%20and%20even%20after%20birth%20--%20execute%20the%20baby%20after%20birth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed%2C%20in%20perhaps%20his%20most%20egregious%20calumny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E78-year-old%20Trump%2C%20now%20the%20oldest%20major-party%20nominee%20in%20history%2C%20is%20scrambling%20to%20reorient%20an%20election%20against%20someone%20two%20decades%20his%20junior%2C%20having%20expected%20to%20face%20an%2081-year-old%20incumbent%20Biden%20beset%20by%20concerns%20over%20infirmity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20last%20week%2C%20the%20former%20reality%20TV%20star%20was%20in%20cruise%20control%20as%20he%20accepted%20a%20hero's%20welcome%20--%20and%20the%20official%20presidential%20nomination%20--%20at%20the%20Republican%20convention%20in%20Milwaukee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrowning%20glory%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20crowning%20glory%20came%20a%20week%20after%20a%20gunman%20nearly%20killed%20him%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Butler%2C%20Pennsylvania%20--%20an%20extraordinary%20incident%20that%20Trump%20vowed%20Friday%20to%20commemorate%20with%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20and%20beautiful%26quot%3B%20new%20rally%20in%20the%20town%2C%20although%20he%20did%20not%20give%20a%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeeking%20to%20become%20the%20first%20female%20president%20in%20US%20history%2C%20Harris%20is%20tasked%20with%20rapidly%20assembling%20a%20campaign%20against%20an%20opponent%20who%20has%20been%20in%20near%20permanent%20reelection%20mode%20since%20he%20became%20president%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20predecessor%20Barack%20Obama%20pledged%20support%20for%20Harris%20earlier%20Friday%2C%20as%20polls%20showed%20her%20closing%20the%20gap%20that%20Trump%20had%20built%20over%20Biden%20to%20make%20the%20race%20a%20statistical%20tie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20top%20California%20prosecutor%20and%20senator%20before%20being%20elected%20the%20country's%20first%20female%20and%20first%20Black%20and%20South%20Asian%20vice%20president%2C%20Harris%20has%20highlighted%20Trump's%20criminal%20conviction%20and%20what%20she%20said%20Thursday%20is%20a%20Republican%20attack%20on%20%26quot%3Bhard-fought%20freedoms%26quot%3B%20in%20US%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20leapt%20on%20a%20Trump%20campaign%20announcement%20late%20Thursday%20that%20cast%20into%20doubt%20whether%20he%20will%20debate%20Harris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20that%20he's%20afraid%2C%26quot%3B%20Transport%20Secretary%20Pete%20Buttigieg%2C%20a%20major%20Harris%20campaign%20advocate%2C%20told%20MSNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20shows%20that%20he%20knows%20that%20if%20the%20two%20of%20them%20are%20on%20a%20stage%20together%2C%20it's%20not%20going%20to%20end%20well%20for%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722061920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fugf3uu1g_trump-harris-_625x300_22_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-calls-kamala-harris-married-to-a-jewish-man-an-anti-semite-6199593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20falsely%20accused%20election%20rival%20Kamala%20Harris%20of%20being%20an%20anti-Semite%20who%20plans%20to%20allow%20the%20murder%20of%20newborn%20babies%2C%20in%20a%20speech%20meant%20to%20rally%20religious%20supporters%20Friday%20that%20quickly%20went%20off%20the%20rails.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-calls-kamala-harris-married-to-a-jewish-man-an-anti-semite-6199593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-calls-kamala-harris-married-to-a-jewish-man-an-anti-semite-6199593%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-calls-kamala-harris-married-to-a-jewish-man-an-anti-semite-6199593%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22American%20support%20for%20female%20president%20falls%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722061905000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-1