d%2C%20Abhishek%2C%20and%20the%20roommate%20frequently%20argued%20about%20his%20unemployment%2C%20and%20these%20disputes%20often%20grew%20intense.%20Kriti%20would%20sometimes%20get%20involved%2C%20and%20end%20up%20making%20the%20situation%20worse.%20Allegedly%2C%20she%20suggested%20that%20her%20roommate%20should%20distance%20herself%20from%20the%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%2C%20however%2C%20soured%2C%20and%20Kriti%20and%20her%20friends%20started%20to%20avoid%20him.%20Sometime%20ago%20Abhishek%20came%20to%20the%20PG%20hostel%20and%20created%20a%20ruckus%20following%20which%20Kriti%20Kumari%20helped%20her%20friend%20shift%20to%20a%20new%20PG%20hostel%2C%20and%20both%20stopped%20taking%20his%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20enraged%20him%20and%20ultimately%20led%20him%20to%20kill%20Kriti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8aej92uo_kriti-kumari-bengaluru-murder_625x300_27_July_24.jpeg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20which%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20shows%20the%20attacker%20walking%20into%20the%20corridor%20of%20the%20paying%20guest%20accommodation%20where%20Kriti%20Kumari%20used%20to%20stay.%20The%20CCTV%20footage%20shows%20Abhishek%20walking%20toward%20Kriti's%20room%20holding%20a%20plastic%20bag%20in%20his%20hand.%20Abhishek%20knocks%20on%20the%20door%20and%20enters%20the%20room.%20Soon%20after%2C%20Abhishek%20is%20seen%20dragging%20her%20out%20and%20Kriti%20struggles%20to%20get%20out%20of%20his%20clutches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%2C%20who%20was%20holding%20a%20knife%20in%20one%20hand%2C%20grabs%20Kriti's%20neck.%20Even%20as%20Kriti%20struggles%20to%20avoid%20being%20stabbed%2C%20the%20killer%20manages%20to%20stab%20her%20repeatedly.%20As%20Kriti%20loses%20the%20strength%20to%20defend%20herself%2C%20the%20killer%20takes%20his%20time%20and%20attacks%20her%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20Kriti%20collapses%2C%20the%20killer%20holds%20her%20by%20the%20hair%20and%20stabs%20her.%20He%20then%20takes%20a%20step%20away%20from%20her%2C%20and%20after%20seeing%20her%20still%20breathing%2C%20he%20tries%20to%20slit%20her%20throat%20again%20before%20running%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKumari%20is%20seen%20sitting%20with%20blood%20on%20her%20chest%20and%20the%20floor.%20Other%20women%20in%20the%20PG%20rushed%20out%2C%20and%20on%20seeing%20her%2C%20one%20of%20them%20was%20seen%20dialling%20on%20her%20cell%20phone%20what%20was%20likely%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722060840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Feup1176g_bengaluru-hostel-murder-cctv_625x300_27_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fin-bengaluru-hostel-murder-police-probe-finds-a-relationship-gone-sour-6199158%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20brutal%20murder%20of%20a%2024-year-old%20woman%20at%20a%20hostel%20in%20a%20posh%20Bengaluru%20locality%20has%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20nation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fin-bengaluru-hostel-murder-police-probe-finds-a-relationship-gone-sour-6199158%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fin-bengaluru-hostel-murder-police-probe-finds-a-relationship-gone-sour-6199158%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbangalore-news%2Fin-bengaluru-hostel-murder-police-probe-finds-a-relationship-gone-sour-6199158%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCat%20Lady%2C%20Brat%26quot%3B%3A%20Media%20Attacks%20On%20Kamala%20Harris%20Follow%20A%20Bleak%20Pattern%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris%20is%20the%20presumptive%20Democratic%20presidential%20nominee.%20And%20while%20she%20will%20not%20be%20the%20Democrat's%20first%20woman%20nominee%2C%20nor%20the%20first%20person%20of%20colour%2C%20she%20faces%20the%20compounding%20challenge%20of%20being%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20will%20be%20subject%20to%20a%20highly%20combative%20and%20partisan%20media%20landscape%2C%20against%20an%20opponent%20who%20pushes%20political%20rhetoric%20to%20the%20extreme.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crucial%20question%20remains%20whether%20the%20media%20can%20fairly%20assess%20her%20qualifications%20for%20office.%20The%20answer%20could%20profoundly%20impact%20women's%20political%20participation%20-%20not%20only%20in%20the%20United%20States%20but%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESexist%2C%20racist%2C%20transphobic%3A%20Past%20media%20treatment%20of%20Harris%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20coverage%20of%20Harris%20to%20date%20reflects%20the%20US'%20s%20deeply%20partisan%20landscape%2C%20with%20Democrat%20and%20Republican%20voters%20consuming%20and%20trusting%20in%20two%20nearly%20inverse%20news%20media%20landscapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20mainstream%20media%20begins%20to%20reckon%20with%20Harris%20as%20the%20presumptive%20nominee%20(The%20New%20York%20Post%20referred%20to%20Harris%20as%20the%20first%20'DEI%20%5Bdiversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%5D%20President'%2C%20so%20we're%20off%20to%20a%20predictable%20start)%2C%20previous%20scrutiny%20%2C%20particularly%20during%20her%20past%20campaigns%2C%20highlights%20persistent%20themes%20of%20sexism%2C%20racism%2C%20and%20conspiracy%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20media%20onslaughts%20echo%20attacks%20faced%20by%20other%20women%20leaders%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202020%20US%20election%2C%20analysis%20of%20online%20discourse%20of%20women%20politicians%20(78%20percent%20of%20which%20was%20directed%20at%20Harris)%20found%20that%20women%20faced%20three%20familiar%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20sexualised%20narratives%20(that%20Harris%20%26quot%3Bslept%20her%20way%20to%20the%20top%26quot%3B).%20Second%2C%20transphobic%20narratives%20(insinuating%20that%20Harris%20was%20secretly%20a%20man).%20And%2C%20third%2C%20racist%20or%20racialised%20narratives%20(whether%20Harris%20was%20suitably%20Black%20or%20Indian%20enough%2C%20or%20even%20whether%20there%20was%20legitimacy%20to%20her%20citizenship%20and%20therefore%20eligibility%20for%20the%20Presidency).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20note%20that%20while%20online%20commentary%20is%20not%20media%20reporting%2C%20the%20distance%20between%20the%20two%20has%20blurred%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20line%20between%20%26quot%3Breporter%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Binfluencer%26quot%3B%20becomes%20less%20distinguishable%2C%20high-profile%20Republican%20commenters%20continue%20to%20post%20unfounded%20aspersions%2C%20such%20as%20Harris%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20black...%5Bbut%5D%20part%20of%20the%20delusional%2C%20Democrat%20DEI%20quota%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20these%20narratives%20then%20seep%2C%20largely%20unquestioned%20%2C%20into%20a%20range%20of%20traditional%20news%20and%20social%20media%20channels%20such%20as%20X%2C%20Donald%20Trump's%20Truth%20Social%2C%20Facebook%2C%20and%20political%20segments%20of%20conservative%20news%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20environment%2C%20misinformation%20and%20disinformation%20thrive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmericans%20are%20simultaneously%20more%20likely%20to%20turn%20to%20social%20media%20for%20their%20news%20and%20are%20less%20critical%20of%20these%20sources%2C%20creating%20an%20environment%20where%20the%20veracity%20of%20gendered%20and%20racialised%20statements%20regarding%20Harris%20is%20less%20important%20than%20their%20virality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMedia's%20history%20of%20misogyny%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%20leaders%20worldwide%2C%20such%20as%20former%20prime%20ministers%20Julia%20Gillard%20in%20Australia%2C%20the%20UK's%20Theresa%20May%20(and%20oh-so-briefly%2C%20Liz%20Truss)%2C%20New%20Zealand's%20Jacinda%20Ardern%20and%20Sanna%20Marin%20in%20Finland%2C%20have%20all%20endured%20misogynistic%20media%20portrayals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20may%20recall%20Gillard's%20opponent%20posing%20with%20%26quot%3BDitch%20the%20Witch%26quot%3B%20placards%2C%20watched%20video%20compilations%20of%20Ardern%20responding%20to%20misogynistic%20questions%2C%20or%20the%20international%20furor%20Marin%20faced%20after%2C%20in%20Fox%20News'%20words%20%2C%20%26quot%3Bgoing%20viral%20for%20%5Ba%5D%20raunchy%20dance%20video...%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20last%20(and%20first)%20major%20party%20woman%20presidential%20nominee%2C%20Hillary%20Clinton%2C%20faced%20a%20similar%20media%20environment%20that%20took%20misogynistic%20cues%20from%20her%20political%20opponent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20protections%20offered%20to%20her%20in%20her%20position%20of%20privilege%20and%20power%2C%20the%20media%20was%20seemingly%20only%20too%20happy%20to%20respond%20to%20Trump's%20calls%20to%20%26quot%3Block%20her%20up%26quot%3B%20with%20a%20series%20of%20investigative%20reports%20into%20the%20Clinton%20Foundation%2C%20her%20tenure%20as%20Secretary%20of%20State%2C%20and%20her%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Black%20and%20South%20Asian%20woman%2C%20Harris%20may%20face%20more%20harassment%20than%20Clinton%2C%20Gillard%2C%20Ardern%20or%20Marin%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20are%20white%20in%20white-majority%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20misogynoir%2C%20coined%20by%20gay%20black%20feminist%20Moya%20Bailey%2C%20aptly%20describes%20a%20%26quot%3Bparticular%20brand%20of%20hatred%20directed%20at%20Black%20women%20in%20American%20visual%20and%20popular%20culture%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%2C%20Harris'%20opponents%20have%20already%20referred%20to%20her%20as%20%26quot%3Baggressive%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3Bangry%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bmean%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20suggested%20she's%20a%20DEI%20nominee%20successful%20for%20the%20novelty%20of%20those%20identities%20rather%20than%20her%20qualifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20media%20reporting%20of%20Harris%20therefore%20continues%20this%20rich%20tradition%20i%20n%20an%20environment%20where%20a%20second%20Trump%20administration%20poses%20a%20grave%20threat%20to%20American%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20consequences%20of%20bias%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBiased%20media%20reporting%20contributes%20to%20real-world%20consequences%2C%20deterring%20women%20and%20marginalised%20people%20from%20entering%20politics%20due%20to%20fears%20of%20online%20harassment%20and%20myriad%20biases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20the%20Global%20Institute%20for%20Women's%20Leadership%20and%20Women%20For%20Election%20in%20Australia%20found%20that%2066%20percent%20of%20women%20polled%20considered%20online%20harassment%20a%20barrier%20to%20running%20for%20office.%20Another%2046%20percent%20said%20bias%20against%20candidates%20from%20a%20marginalised%20background%20was%20an%20additional%20deterrent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20politically%20engaged%20people%20also%20see%20workplace%20safety%20-%20meaning%20spaces%20free%20of%20violence%2C%20misogyny%2C%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20discrimination%20-%20as%20crucial%20to%20their%20engagement%20in%20a%20political%20career.%3Cbr%3E%5CnLong%20before%20the%20attempted%20assassination%20of%20Trump%2C%20the%20personal%20safety%20of%20political%20candidates%20has%20been%20a%20key%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20perception%20of%20politics%20as%20hostile%20and%20unsafe%20(also%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Btoxic%20parliaments%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20new%20book%20launched%20by%20ANU's%20Global%20Institute%20for%20Women's%20Leadership%20last%20week)%20further%20erodes%20trust%20in%20political%20institutions%20and%20discourages%20young%20people%20from%20pursuing%20political%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoung%20women%20and%20other%20minority%20groups%20do%20not%20have%20the%20Secret%20Service%20protecting%20them%20when%20they%20run%20for%20local%20office%2C%20but%20those%20politics%20remain%20as%20vitriolic%20-%20and%20are%20far%20more%20accessible%20-%20than%20the%20Oval%20Office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conditions%20in%20which%20Harris%20obtained%20the%20nomination%20also%20matters.%3Cbr%3E%5CnWith%20an%20ageing%20President%20polling%20much%20lower%20than%20his%20opponent%2C%20a%20turbulent%20domestic%20economy%2C%20and%20the%20highly%20criticised%20support%20of%20Israel's%20war%20on%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20Biden's%20passing%20of%20the%20baton%20to%20Harris%20recalls%20the%20%26quot%3Bglass%20cliff%26quot%3B%20phenomenon%20whereby%20women%20are%20promoted%20to%20leadership%20at%20%26quot%3Bparticularly%20precarious%20times%26quot%3B%20-%20for%20instance%20in%20periods%20of%20crisis%2C%20or%20where%20the%20chance%20of%20failure%20is%20high.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20conditions%20matter%2C%20as%20they%20will%20become%20inextricably%20tied%20to%20the%20story%20of%20Harris'%20run%20for%20president%20and%20embedded%20into%20any%20number%20of%20explanations%20or%20justifications%20as%20to%20why%20her%20campaign%20succeeded%20or%20failed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProgress%2C%20or%20just%20holding%20the%20line%20for%20women%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Harris%20loses%20in%20November%2C%20Trump's%20administration%20is%20slated%20to%20implement%20and%20accelerate%20policies%20that%20undermine%20the%20rights%20of%20women%20and%20minorities%20on%20issues%20including%20abortion%2C%20immigration%2C%20education%20and%20voting%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20this%20agenda%20will%20have%20far-reaching%20consequences%20for%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20galvanising%20illiberal%20governments%20world-wide%20which%20are%20implementing%20populist%2C%20anti-rights%20agendas.%3Cbr%3E%5CnYet%2C%20even%20if%20Trump%20fails%20and%20Harris%20becomes%20the%20next%20US%20President%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20gendered%2C%20racialised%20mess%20of%20media%20reporting%20is%20not%20a%20blip%2C%20but%20a%20characteristic%20of%20our%20media%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20media%20conglomerates%20and%20everyday%20keyboard%20warriors%20have%20an%20effect%20on%20gendered%20and%20racialised%20bias%20among%20voters.%20Reporters%2C%20at%20least%2C%20should%20be%20held%20to%20minimum%20standards%20to%20do%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20reporting%2C%20the%20events%20of%20the%20last%20few%20years%20have%20revealed%20the%20vulnerabilities%20of%20the%20American%20democratic%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhether%20Harris%20succeeds%20or%20fails%20%2C%20she%20faces%20an%20enormous%20burden%20to%20simply%20hold%20the%20line%2C%20let%20alone%20prevent%20regression%20along%20a%20host%20of%20domains%20from%20social%20to%20economic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20be%20the%20work%20of%20decades%20to%20not%20only%20patch%20up%20the%20cracks%2C%20but%20to%20envision%20and%20build%20a%20system%20that%20is%20fairer%2C%20safer%20and%20more%20accessible%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20who%20is%20up%20to%20the%20task%2C%20if%20not%20women%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJack%20Hayes%20is%20a%20PhD%20candidate%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20International%20Relations%20in%20the%20Coral%20Bell%20School%20of%20Asia%20Pacific%20Affairs%20at%20the%20Australian%20National%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Elise%20Stephenson%20is%20a%20multi%20award-winning%20Australian%20gender%20researcher%20and%20entrepreneur%2C%20and%20Deputy%20Director%20at%20the%20Global%20Institute%20for%20Women's%20Leadership%20at%20the%20Australian%20National%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOriginally%20published%20under%20Creative%20Commons%20by%20360info.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722060720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fabgcje7_kamal