mong%20others%20during%20a%202021%20interview%20and%20said%20those%20without%20offspring%2C%20especially%20%26quot%3Bchildless%20cat%20ladies%26quot%3B%2C%20had%20no%20%26quot%3Bdirect%20stake%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20Tucker%20Carlson%20on%20Fox%20News%2C%20he%20had%20said%20the%20US%20was%20being%20run%20by%20%26quot%3Ba%20bunch%20of%20childless%20cat%20ladies%20who%20are%20miserable%20at%20their%20own%20lives%20and%20the%20choices%20that%20they've%20made%20and%20so%20they%20want%20to%20make%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%20miserable%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance's%20comments%20have%20drawn%20sexism%20charges%20ahead%20of%20the%20US%20Presidential%20elections%20that%20the%20Republicans%20were%20touted%20to%20win%20until%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20bowed%20out%20from%20the%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamala%20Harris's%20lack%20of%20biological%20children%20has%20been%20regarded%20as%20an%20issue%20by%20the%20Republicans%2C%20but%20she%20has%20received%20support%20from%20politicians%2C%20celebrities%2C%20and%20from%20her%20own%20family.%20Her%20supporters%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20no%20US%20president%20has%20ever%20physically%20given%20birth%2C%20since%20all%20have%20been%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerstin%20Emhoff%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20Harris'%20stepchildren%2C%20has%20slammed%20the%20attacks%20on%20the%20Vice%20President%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20CNN.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20over%2010%20years%2C%20since%20Cole%20and%20Ella%20were%20teenagers%2C%20Kamala%20has%20been%20a%20co-parent%20with%20Doug%20and%20I.%20I%20love%20our%20blended%20family%20and%20am%20grateful%20to%20have%20her%20in%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance%2C%2039%2C%20was%20tapped%20by%20Trump%20days%20after%20a%20failed%20assassination%20attempt%20on%20the%20former%20president%20upended%20what%20had%20already%20been%20a%20chaotic%20presidential%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722055680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fenv6pf5g_jd-vance_625x300_26_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjd-vance-vs-kamala-harris-jd-vance-defends-childless-cat-ladies-remark-amid-huge-backlash-6198858%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JD%20Vance%2C%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20running%20mate%2C%20has%20defended%20his%202021%20remarks%20where%20he%20referred%20to%20Democratic%20politicians%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bbunch%20of%20childless%20cat%20ladies%20with%20miserable%20lives%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjd-vance-vs-kamala-harris-jd-vance-defends-childless-cat-ladies-remark-amid-huge-backlash-6198858%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjd-vance-vs-kamala-harris-jd-vance-defends-childless-cat-ladies-remark-amid-huge-backlash-6198858%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjd-vance-vs-kamala-harris-jd-vance-defends-childless-cat-ladies-remark-amid-huge-backlash-6198858%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Children%20Of%20Indian-American%20Immigrants%20Face%20Deportation%20As%20Time%20Runs%20Out%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20any%20light%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20for%20children%20of%20legal%20immigrants%2C%20a%20significantly%20large%20number%20of%20whom%20are%20Indian-Americans%20who%20came%20to%20the%20US%20as%20a%20young%20kid%20with%20their%20parents%20and%20now%20risk%20being%20deported%20back%20to%20the%20country%20where%20they%20don't%20know%20anyone%20because%20of%20them%20being%20aging%20out%20when%20they%20turn%2021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20around%20250%2C000%20of%20such%20children%20of%20legal%20immigrants%2C%20a%20significantly%20large%20number%20of%20whom%20are%20Indians.%20The%20White%20House%20on%20Thursday%20blamed%20the%20Republicans%20for%20this%20legislative%20impasse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20talked%20about%20the%20bipartisan%20agreement%20that%20came%20together%20from%20the%20Senate%20where%20we%20negotiated%20a%20process%20to%20help%20the%20so-called%20documented%20Dreamers.%20And%20sadly%2C%20Republicans%2C%20and%20I've%20said%20this%20many%20times%20already%20at%20this%20podium%20today%2C%20which%20is%20that%20they%20voted%20it%20down%20twice.%20They%20voted%20it%20down%20twice%2C'%20White%20House%20Press%20Secretary%20Karine%20Jean-Pierre%20told%20reporters%20at%20her%20daily%20news%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20led%20by%20Senator%20Alex%20Padilla%2C%20Chair%20of%20the%20Senate%20Judiciary%20Subcommittee%20on%20Immigration%2C%20Citizenship%2C%20and%20Border%20Safety%2C%20and%20Representative%20Deborah%20Ross%2C%20a%20bipartisan%20group%20of%2043%20lawmakers%20called%20on%20Biden%20Administration%20to%20take%20urgent%20action%20to%20protect%20the%20more%20than%20250%2C000%20Documented%20Dreamers%20-%20children%20of%20long-term%20visa%20holders%20-%20who%20are%20at%20risk%20of%20aging%20out%20of%20their%20dependent%20status%20and%20are%20forced%20to%20self-deport%20if%20they%20are%20ineligible%20for%20another%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20young%20people%20grow%20up%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20complete%20their%20education%20in%20the%20American%20school%20system%2C%20and%20graduate%20with%20degrees%20from%20American%20institutions%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20the%20lawmakers.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20due%20to%20the%20long%20green-card%20backlog%2C%20families%20with%20approved%20immigrant%20petitions%20are%20often%20stuck%20waiting%20decades%20for%20permanent%20resident%20status%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Biden%20Administration%20on%20June%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Improve%20The%20Dream%2C%20an%20organization%20representing%20these%20children%20of%20legal%20immigrants%2C%20met%20with%20over%20100%20congressional%20offices%20and%20senior%20administration%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20disappointing%20to%20see%20the%20lack%20of%20action%20and%20associated%20proposed%20regulations%20deprioritized%20and%20delayed.%20It%20is%20time%20for%20action%20and%20I%20hope%20President%20Biden%20and%20the%20administration%20see%20the%20support%20from%20this%20bipartisan%20letter%20and%20show%20they%20care%20about%20one%20of%20the%20most%20bipartisan%20issues%20in%20Congress%20and%20rectify%20the%20mistakes%20of%20the%20past%2C'%20said%20Dip%20Patel%2C%20founder%20of%20Improve%20The%20Dream%20comments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20the%20bipartisan%20members%20of%20Congress%20leading%20in%20a%20letter%20asking%20for%20urgent%20administrative%20policy%20improvements%20and%20who%20continue%20to%20champion%20a%20permanent%20solution%20through%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20forced%20to%20start%20visa-hopping%20to%20be%20able%20to%20stay%20in%20this%20country%20when%20I%20was%2020%20years%20old%2C%20right%20before%20I%20aged%20out%2C%20as%20a%20junior%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Minnesota%20-%20Duluth.%20I%20am%20about%20to%20turn%2027%20this%20August.%20Soon%2C%20if%20my%20time%20visa-hopping%20was%20personified%2C%20they%20would%20be%20older%20than%20I%20was%20when%20I%20first%20came%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20Jefrina%2C%20currently%20a%20graduate%20student%20pursuing%20my%20MBA%20at%20the%20Saint%20Mary's%20University%20of%20Minnesota%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20came%20to%20the%20US%20from%20India%20in%202005%20at%20the%20age%20of%207.%20%26quot%3BI%20arrived%20under%20a%20dependent%20H-4%20visa.%20My%20family%20applied%20for%20permanent%20residency%20in%202010%20when%20I%20was%2012%20years%20old%2C%20and%20I%20unwittingly%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20this%20country.%20In%20the%20last%2019%20years%2C%20Minnesota%20has%20undoubtedly%20become%20my%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20young%20adult%20life%20has%20been%20a%20series%20of%20temporary%20fixes%20to%20avoid%20self-deportation.%20I%20graduate%20from%20my%20Masters%20program%20in%20December%2C%20and%20I'm%20yet%20again%20at%20the%20crossroads%20of%20leaving%20my%20family%2C%20pets%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20a%20myriad%20of%20unquantifiable%20reasons%20I%20call%20Minnesota%20my%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Jefrina%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPraneetha%2C%20a%20Cloud%20Engineer%20based%20in%20Texas%2C%20who%20came%20to%20the%20US%20with%20her%20family%20when%20she%20was%208%20years%20old%20as%20a%20dependent%20on%20her%20parents'%20work%20visa%2C%20and%20after%20living%20in%20the%20US%20for%20more%20than%2015%20years%2C%20is%20left%20with%20no%20clear%20path%20toward%20permanent%20residency%20and%20has%20to%20hop%20from%20visa%20to%20visa%20in%20order%20to%20continue%20living%20and%20working%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoshan%20was%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20US%20last%20month.%20He%20was%20working%20with-%20an%20American%20semiconductor%20manufacturing%20company.%20He%20came%20to%20the%20US%20with%20his%20Mom%20and%20brother%20at%20the%20age%20of%2010%20on%20an%20H4%20visa-%20he%20grew%20up%20in%20Boston%20and%20graduated%20from%20Boston%20College%20in%202021%20with%20a%20degree%20in%20Economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoshan%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20US%20for%20almost%2016%20years%20but%20aged%20out%20in%202019.%20He%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20US%20in%20June%20without%20a%20clear%20path%20for%20returning%2C%20living%2C%20and%20working%20in%20the%20only%20country%20that%20he%20has%20truly%20called%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatel%20said%20every%20day%20without%20action%20results%20in%20young%20adults%2C%20who%20have%20been%20lawfully%20raised%20in%20the%20United%20States%20by%20skilled%20workers%20and%20small%20business%20owners%2C%20to%20be%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20country%2C%20separating%20them%20from%20their%20families%20and%20stopping%20their%20ability%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20has%20heard%20countless%20stories%20and%20examples%20of%20American-raised%20and%20educated%20STEM%20and%20health%20care%20talent%20(which%20comprises%2087%25%20of%20all%20impacted%20by%20aging-out%2C%20according%20to%20Improve%20The%20Dream's%20survey)%20contributing%20in%20other%20countries%20now%20due%20to%20barriers%20in%20our%20legal%20immigration%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20country%20is%20not%20only%20losing%20young%20talent%20who%20were%20raised%20and%20educated%20here%2C%20but%20we're%20also%20losing%20many%20of%20their%20parents%2C%20who%20have%20years%20of%20practical%20experience%20as%20small%20business%20owners%20or%20in%20fields%20like%20medicine%2C%20engineering%2C%20and%20artificial%20intelligence.%20The%20economic%20case%20is%20clear%20and%20the%20moral%20case%20is%20clear.%20It%20is%20common%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20major%20administrative%20actions%20have%20excluded%20this%20population%20from%20receiving%20benefit%2C%20despite%20the%20tools%20for%20such%20relief%20being%20available%20and%20being%20used%20for%20others.%20Until%20Congress%20can%20pass%20the%20bipartisan%20America's%20Children%20Act%2C%20we%20need%20urgent%20action%20by%20the%20administration%20to%20prioritize%20this%20issue%2C%20which%20has%20bipartisan%20support%20from%20Congress%20and%20the%20general%20public%2C%20and%20clear%20economic%20benefit%2C%26quot%3B%20Patel%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722055140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-04%2F