ed%20resistance%20from%20villagers%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20life%20inspired%20the%20Aamir%20Khan-starrer%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20Dangal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20girls%20to%20enter%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20a%20male%20domain%2C%20was%20met%20with%20significant%20opposition%20in%20his%20village%20Balali%20in%20Charkhi%20Dadri%20district%20(then%20in%20Bhiwani).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20almost%20a%20year-and-a-half%20later%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20allow%20girls%20to%20train%20alongside%20boys%20at%20Chotu%20Ram%20Stadium%20Wrestling%20Centre%20in%20Rohtak%20faced%20societal%20hurdles.%20Former%20wrestlers%2C%20and%20even%20some%20coaches%2C%20expressed%20reservations%2C%20questioning%20%E2%80%9Chow%20goats%20could%20stay%20among%20the%20lions%E2%80%9D%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20girls%20would%20distract%20boys%2C%20leading%20to%20indiscipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202024.%20What%20was%20once%20met%20with%20sarcasm%E2%80%94people%20comparing%20girls%20to%20goats%20and%20boys%20to%20lions%2C%20emphasising%20the%20perceived%20disparity%20in%20strength%20and%20prowess%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena%E2%80%94has%20now%20become%20a%20point%20of%20pride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20flag%20bearers%20of%20Indian%20wrestling%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffarmers-daughter-set-to-rock-paris-olympics-archery-shorts-parisolympics2024-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Paris%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20is%20represented%20by%20six%20wrestlers%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%2C%20where%20they%20once%20faced%20stiff%20opposition%20to%20entering%20the%20male-dominated%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20c