0father%E2%80%99s%20idea%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20plant%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Etoo%2C%20he%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CMany%20were%20inspired%20after%20seeing%20our%20plantation%20and%20took%20plants%20from%20us.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20we%20have%20distributed%20around%202%2C00%2C000%20saplings%20to%20interested%20farmers.%20We%20charged%20Rs%205%20to%2012%20per%20sapling%2C%20but%20we%20stopped%20nursery%20production%20to%20prevent%20oversaturation%20in%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Ramesh%20worked%20as%20a%20hotelier%20for%20most%20of%20his%20life%2C%20he%20is%20now%20planning%20to%20take%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%3Cbr%3Elegacy%20ahead.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20was%20always%20dedicated%20to%20farming%2C%20and%20he%20started%20the%20hotel%20business%20too%20managing%20it%20alongside%20the%20plantation.%20The%20land%20was%20ancestral%20but%20it%20was%20my%20father%20who%20expanded%20it%20to%20200%20sq%20ft%20and%20turned%20it%20into%20a%20farm%20estate.%20We%20live%20on%20the%20estate%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20divide%20my%20time%20between%20the%20hotel%20and%20the%20plantation%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20his%20future%20plans%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBy%20next%20year%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20focus%20on%20harvesting%20and%20marketing%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20larger%20quantities.%20Labour%20shortages%20have%20limited%20our%20capacity%2C%20but%20we%20are%20addressing%20this%20issue%20by%20bringing%20in%20more%20workers.%20We%20aim%20to%20meet%20the%20current%20high%20market%20demand%20for%20%3Cem%3Ekokum%3C%2Fem%3E.%20This%20year%2C%20we%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20harvest%20much%20due%20to%20labour%20shortages%2C%20but%20with%20new%20labour%20strategies%2C%20we%20hope%20to%20overcome%20this%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20made%20various%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F199656%2Flife