0timely%20advances%20and%20full%20payment%20upon%20order%20completion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20income%20has%20increased%20significantly.%20Fulfilling%20one%20batch%20of%20orders%20in%201.5%20to%20two%20months%20has%20tripled%20our%20monthly%20income%20compared%20to%20before.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-47-1721394923.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20artisans%2C%20mostly%20women%2C%20handle%20every%20production%20step%2C%20ensuring%20each%20Swadeshi%20Blessings%20product%20meets%20high-quality%20standards.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-47-1721394923.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-47-1721394923-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-47-1721394923-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-47-1721394923-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-47-1721394923-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357770%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20artisans%2C%20mostly%20women%2C%20handle%20every%20production%20step%2C%20ensuring%20each%20Swadeshi%20Blessings%20product%20meets%20high-quality%20standards.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20focusing%20on%20clay%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F206013%2Fhow-to-use-season-seasoned-soapstone-cookware-health-benefits-order-online-lifestyle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%2