s%20one-on-one%20sign%20language%20were%20held%20at%20the%20event.%20With%20a%20focus%20on%20promoting%20empathy%20and%20understanding%2C%20Vividhataa%20plans%20to%20make%20DEI%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20Indian%20organisations%20and%20global%20MNCs%20across%20India%20through%20its%20initiative.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20hit%20in%202020%20and%20traditional%20job%20fairs%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20place%20due%20to%20the%20lockdown%2C%20Vividhataa%20filled%20the%20gap%20by%20launching%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%201st%20Virtual%20Diversity%20Job%20Fair%202020%E2%80%9D%20to%20support%20minority%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20fair%20saw%20lots%20of%20diverse%20candidates%20submitting%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20to%20potential%20employers%20and%20becoming%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20in%20an%20otherwise%20challenging%20job%20market.%20Some%20celebrated%20promising%20job%20offers%2C%20while%20others%20prepared%20for%20successive%20rounds%20of%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20got%20employed%20with%20Amazon%20through%20the%20fair.%20Since%20they%20were%20working%20from%20places%20where%20Amazon%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20offices%2C%20they%20were%20given%20WFH%20opportunities.%20A%20laptop%2C%20a%20table%2C%20and%20every%20other%20work%20equipment%20that%20they%20might%20need%20were%20also%20provided%20by%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20word%20of%20the%20job%20fair%20had%20spread%20around%2C%20organisations%20which%20previously%20were%20not%20big%20on%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20had%20shown%20up%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20long-term%20impact%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20on%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisha%20says%20that%20to%20her%20knowledge%2C%20there%20are%20two%20more%20organisations%20that%20work%20for%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20in%20south