echnology%20to%20recycle%20all%20wastes%20into%20fertilisers.%20Key%20components%20of%20this%20system%20include%20intercropping%2C%20advanced%20irrigation%20systems%2C%20and%20efficient%20recycling%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20three%20major%20issues%20in%20farming%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoil%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWaste%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20build%20an%20integrated%20farm%2C%20Saravanan%20first%20added%20a%20dairy%20farm%20with%2020%20cows.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20the%20output%20(dung)%20given%20by%20the%20cows%20that%20he%20designed%20the%20entire%20farm.%20The%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20are%20converted%20into%20natural%20fertilisers%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Epanchagavya%2C%20jeevamruth%2C%20amirtha%20karaisal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20vermicompost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20answers%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20are%20present%20in%20traditional%20farming.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20efforts%20of%20my%20forefathers%20and%20father%20in%20building%20this%20farm%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20waste.%20Farmers%20have%20been%20practising%20soil%20conservation%20and%20balancing%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20ages.%20I%20use%20their%20knowledge%20with%20a%20small%20twist%20of%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20the%20fertilisers%20manually%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20biodigester%2C%20which%20produces%20seven%20times%20the%20output%20that%20was%20being%20produced%20earlier.%20All%20the%20waste%20generated%20in%20the%20cow%20shed%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20fermentation%20chamber%2C%20generating%20almost%207%2C000%20litres%20of%20fertilisers%20daily%2C%20as%20per%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram